Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was quite a bit of talk about it on the way here from Lubinheigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, how creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the sorcerer who appeared on the new road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it can summon wolves to be its puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They attack travelers in order to consume their blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no joke. You better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In Lubinheigen, I heard the rumors from a member of the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,An entire caravan was attacked two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, creepy... Really creepy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drown this fear with more booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't hurt for me to take note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray, for your sake, that the sorcerer isn't a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're easily fooled by women,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and slow to recover when you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been drinking more heavily ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the talk of nearly every tavern we visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Medio Trading deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Men really are dumb creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me for being dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and a Proper Balance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What an inconsiderate town this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They close the tavern far too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is a satellite of the Church stronghold Lubinheigen, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Be thankful they let someone run a tavern for travelers at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So this town's only interested in living a humble life and offering prayers to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:43.87,Default,,1,1,0,,It's best known for the citizens putting you to sleep with talk about how profound the latest sermon was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe anyone could enjoy a life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head to Lubinheigen once I sell the pepper and purchase new goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a large town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bigger than Pazzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a city rather than a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a busy place with lots of street stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will there be any apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about raw apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the season for preserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Preserves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about pickled goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruits preserved in honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just apples, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pears preserved in honey taste good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they started doing peaches recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinly sliced peaches are stacked inside a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The best products even have figs and almonds inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginger is added after honey is poured on the peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They stew for two months like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweet sensation that fills your mouth is unlike anything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not surprising that the Church was considering banning the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not toying with me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not, but peach preserves are a product of the wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really find them just up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if we do? Could we buy them if we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I'll buy some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where else? We'll go to the inn, get our cart, and go to Whatever Trading Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to wake the person there, get good money for our pepper, and head to Lubinheigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. At this hour of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It might sell out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a total catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The market probably won't have them on sale in the first place, let alone sell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Peaches and honey... That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind-boggling, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat this like a sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to give up pears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The pastor's sermons moved our hearts quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was literally a blessing from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,His words gave us motivation to strive for greater service to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I rambled on a bit there, but shall we start discussing our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to offer today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know your goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's just a matter of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to have your own scale, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one, but I have faith in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, what bad luck for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The demand for pepper has increased significantly as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had come a week earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have taken it off your hands for nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like I came in at just the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Let's proceed with the weighing of the pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, we'll need paper and ink.\NWait just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will water be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some wine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, water, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's forty-five measures' worth, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this pepper come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramapata, in the Kingdom of Leedon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Milone Trading conducted the import.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramapata is famous for its spices,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the certificate looks to be genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one Lumione gold coin per measure sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the exchange rate for Lumione gold coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want the value in Trenni silver coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-two and five-sixths Trenni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the current exchange rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A long journey will tire even a strong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring some goat milk for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These scales still seem tilted to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they look that way to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that certainly couldn't be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it couldn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes don't seem to be working correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that what I drank was wine, not water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As the proverb says, "The rowdier the pub, the more sober its master."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret to success is being the only sober one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm drunk on the same wine as my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we'll remember some of the things we've seen and heard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, drunkards have been known to demand unreasonable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay the initial sum you offered, the amount you were to profit from this deal, and, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll allow me to buy double all that on loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Double? That's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like the wine is wearing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the large sum involved here, why don't you pay me in high quality weapons and armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Arms, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always a good bet for turning a safe profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get the loan back to you quickly that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you've got arms bound for Lubinheigen, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Arms, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have connections to other trading companies in Lubinheigen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Selling them there will balance out the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you arrange for the goods immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to leave for Lubinheigen as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the appraisal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that to you. After all, I have faith in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beautiful, I'm wise, and my tail's fur is sleek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But my eyes and ears are also keen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed as soon as I set foot inside this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience may lead to self-confidence, but pride goes before a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Chloe teach you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go sulking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from the experience and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I hear it's good for grooming my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you buy some for me when we reach the next town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The clothes you're wearing now, your change of clothes, your comb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your traveling expenses, food, and the {\i1}huge{\i0} amount of wine... have you bothered to add all that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the head tax I have to pay every time we enter a town, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you're not telling me you can't do sums.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at subtraction, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, add up what you've used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're such a wise wolf, you should be able to work out my answer from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll buy me some for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look what happens to the wits of the proud wise wolf when she has too much wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:42.46,Default,,1,1,0,,Surely you don't think I missed how much you gained\Nfrom taking advantage of that appraiser's weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you buy me some oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much money you still owe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred and forty silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you realize that's a small fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to spend even more on luxuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want me to repay my debt that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of. Course. I. Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose if I pay my debts, that makes me a free wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I suppose I should pay you back as soon as possible and head back north myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm accustomed to solitude, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't decide the due date for payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine so long as I get it before we reach the northern woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I should think I'll be able to repay you by the time we reach the north country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's my intention to pay you back with interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the more I borrow, the greater profit for you. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can put it on my tab,\Nso could you buy some for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day for grooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:46.92,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,By the way, you got quite the discount on those goods, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't want to sponge off a traveling merchant who's barely scraping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Arms sell fast in Lubinheigen, but there are many merchants who sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a lot of profit to be had,\Nso getting a lower price can only do so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you bought this much, will you not make some profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it should cover the cost of some oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in comparison to this load, spices are divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like you, you glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you trade spices again, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Their prices in Lubinheigen aren't much higher than in Poroson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take a loss from selling spices due to tariffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give it up, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could sell other commodities at the same profit margin as spices,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be able to open a store in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jewels and gold seem like they'd sell well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kinds of items aren't too profitable in Lubinheigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The tariff is way too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They levy serious taxes on all but a certain group of merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no business to be had there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are certain merchants exempt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They have ties with the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They bring gold bars to Lubinheigen, and those bars are inscribed with the Holy Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the gold becomes blessed that way, it fetches an absurdly high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Church receives generous donations in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a corrupt system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're extremely strict about smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Smuggled gold would probably sell for twice the market price, but there are too many risks involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any idiots dumb enough to take their chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could gold really be that hard to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Their cargo inspections are pretty thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to those who are caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll cut off your right hand, at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It just isn't worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your business is doing well enough. There's nothing wrong with making steady coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I tend to agree, but a certain someone's spending all my hard-earned money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be careful along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like mercenaries have arrived from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercenaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveling on this path would be suicide, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they spot their prey faster than a hawk on the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and take everything of value, down to the leaves on the turnips.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're armed with long spears, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I have stories to tell about the trouble they've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to hear that they've come this far south.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as us merchants, they only move based on profit and loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's pointless to think about it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's head to Lubinheigen by using the new side road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid of pagan sorcerers, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They say there are packs of wolves on the side route.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're easier to deal with than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I can reason with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the negotiations to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors of a thing usually hold more power than the thing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring. I'm going to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice wolves approaching even if you're asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a hassle if they surround us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Most animals are quite aware, be they sleeping or awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only you humans who are defenseless in slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be more convincing if you snored less.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that loud, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't snore at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you handle these negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's ahead of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of human that I despise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the sorcerer we've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ritual for when you meet a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we know he isn't a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lawrence, a traveling merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my partner, Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask the shepherd I've met under God's guidance to offer prayers for our safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:44.39,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode: "Wolf and the Shepherd's Lamb."
